OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBright or sunny intervals and a
OL,6,Ffew showers this morning. Becoming
OL,7,Fmainly dry and rather cloudy this
OL,8,Fafternoon, chance of a little rain in
OL,9,Fthe south and west late afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be cloudy
OL,12,Fwith outbreaks of rain spreading
OL,13,Fnortheast. Then rain overnight before
OL,14,Fdrier weather spreads to all but the
OL,15,Ffar east later. Fresh southerly winds.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FRain in the east soon
OL,18,Fclearing. Then sunny spells and
OL,19,Fscattered showers, occasionally heavy
OL,20,Fby afternoon. Blustery southwesterly
OL,21,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
